<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>382</hymn_number>
<author>mlḥm dẖhbyẗ, lḥn ạ̉jnby</author>
<title>ʿny qḍy̱ rby ạlḥnwn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ʿny qḍy̱ rby ạlḥnwn .. wdẖạq gẖṣạt ạlmnwn
 mḥrraⁿạ ạ̉sry ạlsjwn .. rb ạlwry̱ fạdy ạlạ̉nạm
 ạlqrạr- jỷt sẖfạʾaⁿ mt fdạʾaⁿ .. fyạ lḥbk ạlʿjyb
 lys swạk ffy dmạk .. njwt mn mwt rhyb
 fkyf ạ̉nsy̱ sẖạfy jrwḥy .. mạḥy ậtẖạmy fkyf ạ̉nsy̱
 lwlạk ạ̉nt ḥby wʿwny .. rby ạ̉nt fy ạlḥsẖạ fln ạ̉nsạk
 2- kyf qḍy̱ yạ llʿjb .. fwq ṣlyb mn kẖsẖb
 bạlṣlb qd mḥy̱ ạlgẖḍb .. wsyṭ ṣlḥ wslạm
 3- sạlt ynạbyʿ dmạh .. ḥbaⁿạ ḥnạnaⁿạ llkẖṭạẗ
 mạ mn rjạʾ bswạh .. ywly ạlkẖlạṣ bạltmạm</lyrics>
</song>